579
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,640
this kind of willpower training?

580
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:16,240
Erpang, to become a man,

581
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:18,840
he needs to be tested.

582
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:23,400
Try this.

583
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:24,520
Can you

584
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:26,040
find him a bedroom?

585
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,080
Become a man.

586
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:28,520
There's space in the bedroom.

587
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:29,800
He can sleep here.

588
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:31,340
It's livelier inside.

589
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:33,500
What about the store downstairs?

590
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:35,640
He can't go out.

591
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:38,200
What if he learns bad habits?

592
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:42,000
He's already here.

593
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:44,760
You're still afraid he'll go out and be corrupted?

594
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,040
Everyone here

595
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:47,700
has been my brother for years.

596
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:49,340
Principled and loyal.

597
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,280
This is his uncle.

598
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:54,760
Say hello to your uncle.

599
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:56,040
Keep playing.

600
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:00,520
You know what?

601
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:03,800
Let him go out and learn bad habits for three years.

602
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,080
See if he can recognize

603
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:07,360
all these brothers of yours.

604
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:09,360
That's absolutely not acceptable.

605
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:10,760
These men have rankings.

606
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:11,880
A kid like him,

607
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,680
how could he possibly meet them?

608
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:14,800
Erpang,

609
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:17,100
pack your things. We're leaving.

610
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:19,080
I've troubled you for so many years.

611
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:20,360
How can I trouble you again?

612
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:21,290
It's no trouble.

613
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,840
Let's go, Erpang.

614
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:24,000
Don't go anywhere.

615
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,360
Just stay here with your father.

616
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:26,760
Come with me now.

617
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:27,680
Fine, you can go.

618
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:29,540
But if you leave, don't come back.

619
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,600
When we get home,

620
00:26:32,600 --> 00:26:34,080
finish your remaining homework quickly

621
00:26:34,080 --> 00:26:35,640
and then have your aunt check it.

622
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,700
I need to go to work.

623
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,920
Is my dad a bad person?

624
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,400
No.

625
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,000
He's not exactly bad,

626
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:47,400
but there might be bad people around him.

627
00:26:48,840 --> 00:26:50,520
I think they're all nice.

628
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,080
They always buy me snacks.

629
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:54,520
Your teacher had a talk with me.

630
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,240
What did they say?

631
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,600
That you've improved in your studies

632
00:26:57,600 --> 00:26:58,680
and get along well with classmates.

633
00:26:58,680 --> 00:26:59,440
Really?

634
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,440
What do you think?

635
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,360
This is what happens when

636
00:27:02,360 --> 00:27:05,240
you spend time with those 'nice people' around your dad.

637
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,080
Listen to me.

638
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:08,640
Until those bad people leave,

639
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:09,800
you can't go back there.

640
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,840
Do you understand?

641
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,880
Manager Cui is our

642
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:20,210
general manager of Dingqing Restaurant.

643
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:23,440
He has accompanied Dingqing

644
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,160
through

645
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:27,080
half a century of ups and downs.

646
00:27:28,080 --> 00:27:29,680
He's also our Dingqing's

647
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:31,980
distinguished general manager.

648
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:33,560
Manager Tang,

649
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:36,440
please seek his guidance in the future.

650
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,900
Manager Cui is truly respected and admired.

651
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,040
Since I was a child, I dreamed

652
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:42,560
that if I could eat here just once a year,

653
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:44,600
how happy I would be.

654
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:46,080
I never imagined

655
00:27:46,080 --> 00:27:48,120
that I would replace you

656
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:49,450
as the general manager.

657
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:52,840
I remember when I was little,

658
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:54,640
I would pass by Dingqing Restaurant every day,

659
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,600
just smelling the aroma

660
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:57,280
would make my mouth water.

661
00:27:58,800 --> 00:28:00,080
A classmate of mine said

662
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:01,880
he had eaten a dish here

663
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,940
called Snow-Covered Red Bean Paste.

664
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:05,360
I was so envious.

665
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:07,000
He told me how

666
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,840
it was prepared.

667
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:10,240
But in the end,

668
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:12,500
I still didn't know what it actually was.

669
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,880
Until the 1980s,

670
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:17,080
when I had been working for several years,

671
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:18,320
I finally had

672
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:20,680
my first taste of Snow-Covered Red Bean Paste.

673
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:22,680
Guess how many I ate?

674
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,640
How many?

675
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:25,000
Eleven.

676
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,680
That's quite a lot.

677
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:29,640
Snow-Covered Red Bean Paste

678
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,880
is the entry-level dish for Dingqing's chefs.

679
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:36,840
It's also the first test for chef evaluation.

680
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:41,240
I see many restaurants nowadays

681
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:44,840
where apprentices become chefs

682
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:47,360
in just three or four years.

683
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:49,860
That's absolutely not acceptable here.

684
00:28:50,840 --> 00:28:54,520
From apprentice to knife skills to chef,

685
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:57,600
even the smartest takes thirteen years.

686
00:28:58,760 --> 00:28:59,840
Most importantly,

687
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:02,080
no matter how many chefs have changed,

688
00:29:02,360 --> 00:29:05,320
the taste of Dingqing's dishes

689
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,520
has never declined.

690
00:29:07,560 --> 00:29:10,280
That shows your excellent management.

691
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:14,320
I'm the second general manager of Dingqing.

692
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,760
The first general manager

693
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:16,920
was Old Mr. Zhang.

694
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,280
This restaurant

695
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:20,800
has been operating for almost a hundred years.

696
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:23,000
Now that this brand is in your hands,

697
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,480
I truly hope

698
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,840
you can make it a century-old establishment.

699
00:29:26,840 --> 00:29:28,640
Don't worry, I absolutely will.

700
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:34,720
The ingredients and chefs are of utmost importance.

701
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:36,880
Let me take you to the kitchen.

702
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:39,000
It's about time now.

703
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:41,560
Let's taste the food together.

704
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:44,400
Please give us your valuable feedback.

705
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,840
This is our signature dish.

706
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:49,440
You must give it a good try.

707
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:51,640
I still don't know

708
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,440
what this Su Huang dish actually is.

709
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:55,680
It's actually just caramelized eggs.

710
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,200
This dish,

711
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,640
though it looks simple,

712
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:00,880
actually...

713
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:04,490
That crazy person making a mess outside earlier,

714
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,560
who is he?

715
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,240
He's talking about Ji Qiang.

716
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,240
That boy,

717
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,320
I heard in the early 80s,

718
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:14,040
he got into college,

719
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,720
but because of some family trouble,

720
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,320
he couldn't attend.

721
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:20,640
The poor kid's mind was traumatized.

722
00:30:21,080 --> 00:30:22,200
What happened?

723
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,080
At first,

724
00:30:23,080 --> 00:30:24,360
he would go to the few

725
00:30:24,360 --> 00:30:25,240
state-owned restaurants in town

726
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,100
to lick plates,

727
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,800
occasionally helping illiterate people

728
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:28,640
write letters

729
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:29,640
to earn some food.

730
00:30:30,360 --> 00:30:31,680
Later when things got better,

731
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,600
he started coming here specifically for leftovers.

732
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:34,640
He's quite peculiar.

733
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:36,160
He doesn't like meat,

734
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,600
he only eats vegetables.

735
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:38,520
So we just

736
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:39,800
take these leftover vegetables,

737
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:40,840
put them together

738
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:41,970
and give them to him.

739
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,600
Won't he being here

740
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:45,920
affect your business?

741
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:46,640
Not at all.

742
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,480
It doesn't affect us one bit.

743
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,480
Manager Tang,

744
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:51,080
you really need to agree to this.

745
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:54,520
Some leftover food

746
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,720
to give him a meal.

747
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:56,850
He's not a nuisance.

748
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:58,560
Life isn't easy.

749
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,720
Manager Cui has spoken,

750
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,160
I must agree.

751
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,720
Besides,

752
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:06,160
I wouldn't dare refuse anyway.

753
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:09,280
Wouldn't dare refuse?

754
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:10,840
What do you mean by that?

755
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,400
Your family members

756
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:14,360
are really too capable.

757
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,760
Talented in both civil and military arts.

758
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:16,800
Thankfully,

759
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:18,930
you only have one son and one daughter.

760
00:31:19,120 --> 00:31:20,720
If you had ten children,

761
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:22,640
all the businesses in the world

762
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,700
would be monopolized by your family.

763
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,290
What do you mean?

764
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,640
Is your son-in-law

765
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,720
named Huo Dongfeng?

766
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:33,320
I suppose so.

767
00:31:33,520 --> 00:31:34,520
You don't know?

768
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:35,880
Know what?

769
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,680
I haven't seen him for many years.

770
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:39,160
Is it true that recently

771
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:41,720
silver carp prices went up by 0.3 yuan per jin?

772
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,780
Yes, prices have gone up everywhere.

773
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:46,280
Now, throughout the city

774
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:48,400
and even the entire province,

775
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,560
all the silver carp

776
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:51,000
are processed by him,

777
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:53,090
making 0.3 yuan profit per jin,

778
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:55,010
and it all goes into his pocket.

779
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:58,040
Your son

780
00:31:58,040 --> 00:32:01,120
is now at the biggest nightclub in our city

781
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:04,040
as their star performer.

782
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:07,080
That's why they say he's talented in every way.

783
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:16,280
Brother, eat up.

784
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:17,720
Thank you, Mengmeng.

785
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,760
That's wonderful, isn't it?

786
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,240
You should cherish your family.

787
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:29,160
Every day your brother spends here.

788
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,560
I've always cherished it.

789
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:32,000
Oh, really?

790
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:35,640
Well.

791
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,480
Come here.

792
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:49,280
Let me see how tall you've grown.

793
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,080
Not good enough.

794
00:32:57,080 --> 00:32:58,240
You need to grow taller quickly.

795
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,080
Look.

796
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:00,810
You're still short.

797
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:01,760
By this much.

798
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,400
For the Xiali car.

799
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:05,480
For our family's Xiali car.

800
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:07,320
I need to grow taller quickly too.

801
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:09,180
Go do your homework after dinner.

802
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,700
Let's go outside and talk.

803
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:15,560
Talk, sure.

804
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,170
Put on your clothes.

805
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,200
What's wrong?

806
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,860
You've really been working hard lately.

807
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:33,320
Yes, as the head of this household,

808
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,640
I wanted to buy a Xiali car sooner.

809
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:39,880
Working night shifts at the factory every day.

810
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:44,330
It's exhausting when your days and nights are reversed.

811
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,460
I've been thinking...

812
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,780
Actually, you didn't really lie.

813
00:33:49,120 --> 00:33:50,520
You said you work night shifts at a factory.

814
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:52,650
If we just rearrange these words a bit,

815
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,810
then it's not really deceiving me.

816
00:33:55,760 --> 00:33:57,690
Because you do work at a nightclub.

817
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:01,020
So that's technically the truth.

818
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:06,280
Cui Guoming!

819
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:09,000
If you've got any guts, never come back!

820
00:34:11,560 --> 00:34:13,120
You bastard!

821
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:23,760
Here, have some soup.

822
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:24,760
Warm yourself up.

823
00:34:35,199 --> 00:34:36,040
Got caught?

824
00:34:37,199 --> 00:34:38,199
What? Got caught?

825
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:40,679
Her husband caught you?

826
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:41,760
Get out of here.

827
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:43,000
I just came from home.

828
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:44,320
We're both men.

829
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,780
You don't need to lie to me.

830
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:48,420
It's good that you managed to escape.

831
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:53,320
Where did Brother Huo go?

832
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,120
He went to a birthday party.

833
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:55,880
Give me...

834
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,080
Find me some of his clothes to try on.

835
00:34:57,080 --> 00:34:58,680
What do you need them for?

836
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,720
Don't worry. You're at home now.

837
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:03,060
If her husband comes, I'll deal with him.

838
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,400
I came from home.

839
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,880
Just hurry up, will you?

840
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:15,360
Look at you, getting all stylish now.

841
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,280
Of course.

842
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,200
This is nice. Good color.

843
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:19,130
I've got to look presentable, bro.

844
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,530
The material is quite good.

845
00:35:28,200 --> 00:35:29,600
Xiao Cui, let me tell you.

846
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,600
This isn't a big deal.

847
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,040
I really came from home.

848
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:47,120
Do you do this often?

849
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:49,740
If you don't tell me the truth,

850
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,480
how can I protect you?

851
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:53,520
Then you tell me the truth first.

852
00:35:54,680 --> 00:35:55,440
Secret.

853
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:13,720
Do you have a crush on him?

854
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:14,480
Get out.

855
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:17,740
Purely professional relationship.

856
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:20,000
I think you two would make a good match.

857
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,520
When he performs on stage,

858
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,820
it's like watching someone welding.

859
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:35,360
There's something I don't understand.

860
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,960
Are you talking to me?

861
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,640
Do you think

862
00:36:45,640 --> 00:36:46,960
you're good-looking?

863
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,680
Not bad. Why?

864
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:50,120
No, no.

865
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:50,920
That's not it.

866
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:53,420
You must think you're very handsome,

867
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,120
otherwise why would you

868
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,680
have your huge face

869
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:57,720
printed this big?

870
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:59,200
The photo is posted here.

871
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,320
Is this photo in color?

872
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,680
Yes.

873
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:05,200
But the only flaw is there's no blush on your cheeks.

874
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:06,240
Never mind that.

875
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:10,080
The photo I hang on the wall is in color.

876
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,840
When yours gets hung on the wall,

877
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,200
it will only be in black and white.

878
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,120
What do you mean?

879
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:15,450
What? You want to fight?

880
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,600
The welder.

881
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:20,890
Ms. Yang wants you to get in the car.

882
00:37:48,120 --> 00:37:49,980
Miss Yang, what do you need me for?

883
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:53,040
It's getting late.

884
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:54,720
I'll take you home.

885
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:57,400
Okay, thanks.

886
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:01,200
Where do you live?

887
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:04,010
The machinery factory dormitory.

888
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:10,960
Is your wife at home?

889
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,080
Yes.

890
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:21,290
I heard you graduated from the Engineering University.

891
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:24,760
People like me who were terrible at school

892
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,960
really admire smart people like you.

893
00:38:28,680 --> 00:38:29,680
I wouldn't call myself smart.

894
00:38:29,680 --> 00:38:32,140
I just did well on the college entrance exam.

895
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:40,160
I've had a bit too much to drink tonight.

896
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,240
Is my face red?

897
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:46,440
No.

898
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,440
Erpang,

899
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:11,880
open the door!

900
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,280
Don't open it.

901
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:30,200
Not many people around today.

902
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,440
I thought you brought Erpang

903
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,440
with you.

904
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,160
It's fine to wait a couple more days.

905
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:37,600
I'll get everything set up for the guys,

906
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,760
then it'll be a good time for him to come.

907
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,160
What's going on with you?

908
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,160
My wife kicked me out.

909
00:41:43,160 --> 00:41:44,690
I'm crashing here tonight.

910
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,360
Move over.

911
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,040
Let's get to work.

912
00:41:48,040 --> 00:41:49,680
Move over. What work are you talking about?

913
00:41:49,680 --> 00:41:50,600
Come over here, let's have a drink.

914
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:51,440
Good.

915
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:58,650
Women need to be coaxed,

916
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,530
and uncles need to be pampered.

917
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:01,880
Women need to be pampered,

918
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:04,680
and you're both coaxing and pampering your uncle.

919
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:08,240
You're asking me for money

920
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,570
because of this, right?

921
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:11,920
I took the lawyer's fee from home.

922
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:13,920
If I can't get it back,

923
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:16,000
my wife is going to fight with me.

924
00:42:16,240 --> 00:42:18,000
Are you sure he didn't kill that person?

925
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,240
Definitely not.

926
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:20,680
This happened because I couldn't keep my mouth shut.

927
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:21,920
I saw his condition

928
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,800
and found a fortune teller

929
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,800
to give him some psychological comfort.

930
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,440
Otherwise, I was afraid something would happen to him.

931
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:27,160
And then this happened.

932
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:29,200
It's my responsibility.

933
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,500
About this matter,

934
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:32,600
if he didn't kill that person himself,

935
00:42:32,600 --> 00:42:33,800
why would he confess?

936
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,360
He not only confessed,

937
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:37,320
he was afraid of being attacked in jail,

938
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,560
so he told everyone in there

939
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:39,680
that he did it.

940
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:43,000
What did the lawyer say?

941
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,040
The lawyer told me

942
00:42:44,040 --> 00:42:46,120
with the current evidence,

943
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:49,360
if he cooperates and shows a good attitude,

944
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:52,420
the lawyer can help him get a suspended death sentence.

945
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:54,650
What kind of lawyer is this?

